Its as if there were a royal frontier city with strong ramparts strong walls  arches and a single gate In it would be a wise competent  intelligent gatekeeper to keep out those he didnt know and to let in those he did
Walking along the path encircling the city he wouldnt see a crack or an opening in the walls big enough for even a cat to slip through
The thought would occur to him Whatever large creatures enter or leave the city all enter or leave it through this gate 
