 The Blessed One acquiesced with silence
Then Ambapl the courtesan understanding the Blessed Ones acquiescence got up from her seat and bowing down to him and circumambulating him left
Then the Licchavis of Vesl heard The Blessed One they say has arrived at Vesl and is staying near Vesl in Ambapls grove
Then having auspicious vehicles yoked the Licchavis got into the auspicious vehicles and left Vesl with the auspicious vehicles
Now some of those Licchavis were dark blue with dark blue complexions dark blue clothing  dark blue ornaments Some of those Licchavis were yellow with yellow complexions yellow clothing  yellow ornaments Some of those Licchavis were red with red complexions red clothing  red ornaments Some of those Licchavis were white with white complexions white clothing  white ornaments
Then Ambapl the courtesan driving axle to axle wheel to wheel yoke to yoke brought those young Licchavis to a halt
So those Licchavis said to her Hey Ambapl what are you doingdriving axle to axle wheel to wheel yoke to yokebringing the young Licchavis to a halt 
