Then the Licchavis delighting in and approving of the Blessed Ones words got up from their seats and bowing down to him and circumambulating him left
Then Ambapl the courtesan at the end of the nightafter having exquisite staple  nonstaple food prepared in her own gardenannounced the time to the Blessed One Its time lord The meal is ready 
Then the Blessed One early in the morning adjusted his lower robe andtaking his bowl  outer robewent together with the Sagha of monks to Ambapl the courtesans meal offering On arrival he sat down on the seat laid out
Ambapl the courtesan with her own hands served  satisfied the Sagha of monks with the Buddha at its head with exquisite staple  nonstaple food
Then when the Blessed One had finished his meal and withdrawn his hand from the bowl Ambapl the courtesan taking a low seat sat to one side
