So nanda you should all live with yourselves as your island yourselves as your refuge with no other as your refuge with the Dhamma as your island the Dhamma as your refuge with no other as your refuge
And how does a monk live with himself as his island himself as his refuge with no other as his refuge with the Dhamma as his island the Dhamma as his refuge with no other as his refuge
