Eight portions of relics there were of him The AllSeeing One Of these seven remained In Jambudlpa with honour
The eighth In Ramagamas kept by naga kings
One tooth the Thirty Gods have kept
Kalingas kings have one the nagas too
They shed their glory oer the fruitful earth
