one in the realm of the king of Kliga another is honored by kings of the ngas
These with their splendor
their excellent gifts embellish this wealthbearing earth
Thus the relics of the One with Vision
are honored by those honored by those who are honored
He is worshiped by deva kings nga kings human kings
and likewise is worshiped by the most excellent people
So pay homage to him with hands palmtopalm over the heart
for the Awakened are rarely encountered in the course of one hundred eons 
Altogether forty teeth and all the headhairs  bodyhairs
