Prince Payasi did not do this and after death at the breakingup of the body he was reborn in the company of the Four Great Kings in the empty Serisaka mansion
whereas the administrator of his charity the young Brahmin Uttara who gave ungrudgingly with his own hands with proper concern and not carelessly was reborn in the company of the ThirtyThree Gods
